The paper discusses training a deep convolutional neural network (CNN) for image classification and object detection in real-time on live video streams with minimal input from a human operator. This falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses object tracking, which falls under robotics (cs.RO) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses weakly-supervised learning, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
